Project Title: Superstore Sales Dashboard Analysis with Power BI

Project Overview: This project involves building a comprehensive sales dashboard using Power BI to visualize sales data for a fictional superstore. The dashboard provides a detailed view of sales performance, profit margins, and shipping modes across different states, categories, and customer segments.

Key Features:

Visual representation of sales by category, sub-category, and shipping mode.
Year-over-year analysis of monthly sales and profit trends.
Geographic distribution of sales and profit, segmented by state.
Segmentation of sales by customer segment and payment mode.
Predictive sales forecasting for the next 15 days based on historical data.
Skills Highlighted:

Power BI for creating interactive dashboards.
Data visualization techniques to highlight key metrics and trends.
Use of time-series forecasting for predictive analysis.
Analyzing geographical and categorical sales data for business insights.
Project Outcome: The dashboard provides business users with a clear understanding of key sales metrics, customer behavior, and delivery performance, allowing for data-driven decision-making to optimize sales strategies and logistics​(Superstore Sales Dashbo…).
